
<p>OpenAI:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Early feedback from the pilot has been positive, so we’re
expanding group chats to all logged-in users on ChatGPT Free, Go,
Plus and Pro plans globally over the coming days. We will continue
refining the experience as more people start using it.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>That didn’t take long — the initial rollout limited to Japan, New Zealand, Korea, and Taiwan started just <a href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2025/11/17/group-chats-in-chatgpt">three days ago</a>.</p>

